Field Detail

ignoreDuplicates

protected boolean ignoreDuplicates
If this is true, duplication checks are performed with the preExistingNodes Map and duplicate entries are ignored. If this is false, duplicate entries in the structure are allowed. Use this setting with caution, as it may cause a StackOverFlowException.

leafConditions

protected Set<Condition<Object>> leafConditions
Conditions that are checked to determine whether a VariableDefinition is a leaf of the Tree.
